headline: Hexagon Agility to deliver fuel systems for X15N natural gas-powered trucks in major Mexican rollout
summary: Hexagon Agility, a business of Hexagon Composites and the world's leading provider of compressed natural gas (CNG/RNG) fuel systems, has received an order for fuel systems for 100 heavy-duty trucks to be operated by Trayecto, the largest trucking company in Mexico.

headline: Europe Diesel Gensets Market Forecast and Company Analysis Report 2025-2033 Featuring Aggreko, Atlas Copco, Ashok Leyland, Caterpillar, Cummins, Cooper, Greaves Cotton, Deere & Co, and Kirloskar
summary: The Europe Diesel Gensets Market is projected to grow significantly, reaching USD 10.31 billion by 2033, from USD 5.69 billion in 2024, exhibiting a CAGR of 6.83% from 2025 to 2033. Key drivers include a rising demand for reliable backup power, expanding industry and commerce, growing data centers, and concerns about grid stability amidst severe weather and renewable energy integration.
